{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/1일차/프로그래머스 실패율/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h3>문제</h3>\n<p>URL : <a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42889\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://programmers.co.kr/learn/courses/30/lessons/42889</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/536b4/problem.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.47916666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/a59e9/problem.webp 192w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/0ca9f/problem.webp 384w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/dc9b9/problem.webp 768w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/b3fdc/problem.webp 983w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/3b721/problem.png 192w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/66595/problem.png 384w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/fe486/problem.png 768w,\n/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/536b4/problem.png 983w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0d2aec57a596b8144ad4eb266d684c1d/fe486/problem.png\"\n            alt=\"문제사진\"\n            title=\"문제사진\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>문제풀이</h3>\n<p>stages 배열을 순회하면서 멈취있는 위치와, 그 이전에 클리어한 스테이지를 각각 카운팅하고, 스테이지의 실패율을 계산하여 정렬하면 문제가 해결될 것이라고 생각해서 접근하였습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import java.util.*;\n\nclass Solution {\n    class Stage {\n        int number;\n        float failRate;\n\n        public Stage(int number, float failRate){\n            this.number = number;\n            this.failRate = failRate;\n        }\n\n        public float getFailRate(){\n            return this.failRate;\n        }\n    }\n\n    public int[] solution(int N, int[] stages) {\n        int[] answer = {};\n        int[] unClearCount = new int[N + 2];\n        int[] tryCount = new int[N + 2];\n\n        Arrays.fill(unClearCount, 0);\n        Arrays.fill(tryCount, 0);\n\n        for(int i = 0; i &lt; stages.length; i++){\n            unClearCount[stages[i]]++;\n            for(int j = 1; j &lt;= stages[i]; j++){\n                tryCount[j]++;\n            }\n        }\n\n        List&lt;Stage> list = new LinkedList();\n        for(int i = 1; i &lt; N + 1; i++){\n            list.add(new Stage(i, (tryCount[i] != 0 ? (float)unClearCount[i] / tryCount[i] : 0)));\n        }\n\n        list.sort((o1, o2)-> {\n            if(Float.compare(o2.failRate, o1.failRate) == 0) {\n                return o1.number - o2.number;\n            }else {\n                return Float.compare(o2.failRate, o1.failRate);\n            }\n        });\n\n        answer = list.stream().mapToInt(stage -> stage.number).toArray();\n\n        return answer;\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Source</h2>\n<p>프로그래머스 코딩 테스트 연습, <a href=\"https://programmers.co.kr/learn/challenges\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://programmers.co.kr/learn/challenges</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"프로그래머스 실패율","summary":"프로그래머스 1단계 실패율 풀이","date":"2022.06.30","categories":["ProblemSolving","구현"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/5bd59c99e302997d1ff9e54d7d966c6d/0f1c0/test.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5bd59c99e302997d1ff9e54d7d966c6d/c898a/test.jpg 160w,\n/static/5bd59c99e302997d1ff9e54d7d966c6d/2278c/test.jpg 320w,\n/static/5bd59c99e302997d1ff9e54d7d966c6d/0f1c0/test.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[]},"width":640,"height":360}},"publicURL":"/static/5bd59c99e302997d1ff9e54d7d966c6d/test.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/1일차/프로그래머스 실패율/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}